trans-unit.source: Specifies the types of framework-level property behavior that pertain to a particular dependency property in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] property system.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvilke typer framework nivå-egenskap som gjelder for en bestemt avhengighetsegenskap i den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] egenskapen system.

trans-unit.source: Use this enumeration when you construct a <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata> instance where you want to specify one or more the framework-level metadata option settings.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne opplisting når du lage en <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>forekomsten der du vil angi én eller flere framework nivå metadata alternativet innstillinger.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>

trans-unit.source: You no longer use this enumeration after the constructor call.
trans-unit.target: Du har ikke lenger bruke denne opplisting etter Konstruktørkall.

trans-unit.source: Instead, query the particular metadata option that was set during registration by checking the `true` or `false` value of a specific property of an existing <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>.
trans-unit.target: I stedet spørringen bestemt metadataene alternativet som ble angitt under registrering av kontroll av `true` eller `false` verdien for en bestemt egenskapen til en eksisterende <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>

trans-unit.source: These property names match the FrameworkPropertyMetadataOptions enumeration values except for NotDataBindable, which is <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.IsNotDataBindable%2A> on the finished <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>.
trans-unit.target: Disse egenskapsnavn samsvarer med FrameworkPropertyMetadataOptions opplistingsverdiene unntatt NotDataBindable, som er <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.IsNotDataBindable%2A>ferdig <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata>.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata> </xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.IsNotDataBindable%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Journal option only specifies the intention to be journaled.
trans-unit.target: Alternativet loggmelding angir bare hensikten skal journaled.

trans-unit.source: The actual journaling may or may not be addressed by journaling services such as those that are present in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] viewer application.
trans-unit.target: Den faktiske loggføringsnivåene kan eller kan ikke løses av loggføringsnivåene tjenester som de som finnes i den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] visningsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: In particular, journaling has some known limitations if the element tree was constructed through code rather than [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Spesielt loggføringsnivåene har noen kjent begrensninger Hvis treet elementet ble konstruert via kode snarere enn [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For details, see [Navigation Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [navigasjon oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Although property value inheritance might appear to work for nonattached dependency properties, the inheritance behavior for a nonattached property through certain element boundaries in the runtime tree is undefined.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Selv om egenskapen verdien arv kan vises til å fungere for ikke-vedlagt avhengighetsegenskaper, Arv virkemåten for ikke-vedlagt egenskapen via grensene enkelte element i treet runtime er ikke definert.

trans-unit.source: Always use <xref:System.Windows.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A> to register properties where you specify <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.Inherits%2A> in the metadata.
trans-unit.target: Bruk alltid <xref:System.Windows.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>til å registrere egenskapene der du angir <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.Inherits%2A>i metadataene.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkPropertyMetadata.Inherits%2A> </xref:System.Windows.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>
